  <brief_title>Hematologic Toxicity Observation of the Docetaxel+ Cisplatin+ Fluorouracil (TPF)Medical Protocol</brief_title>
  <acronym>OTOHTPF</acronym>
  <official_title>Hematologic Toxicity Observation of the TPF Medical Protocol. Description of the Impact of Febrile Neutropenia in Patients Who Receive the Chemotherapy of the TPF Medical Protocol in Head and Neck Cell Carcinoma</official_title>
